Function Reference/comment author IP « WordPress Codex
-----------

Displays the comment author's [IP
address](/Glossary#IP_address "Glossary"). This tag must be within [The
Loop](/The_Loop "The Loop"), or a comment loop.

Use
[get\_comment\_author\_IP](/index.php?title=Template_Tags/get_comment_author_IP&action=edit&redlink=1 "Template Tags/get comment author IP (page does not exist)")
to retrieve the value.

Usage
-----

`  <?php comment_author_IP($comment_ID); ?> `

Example
-------

Posted from: \<?php comment\_author\_IP(); ?\>

Parameters
----------

 `comment_ID` 
:   ([*integer*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#Integer "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) The ID of the comment for which to print the author's
    IP address.
    Default: *None*

Changelog
---------

-    ? : Added the 'comment\_ID' parameter.
-   Since: 0.71

